          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1670922312179-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1670922312179-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1670922312179-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Chop your<strong> chestnut mushrooms </strong>into quarters</p><p>Chop your <strong>smoked streaky bacon</strong> into rough, bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1670922316204-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1670922316204-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1670922316204-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1670922316204-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1670922316204-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Line a baking tray (or two!) with a large piece of <strong>tin foil</strong></p><p>Trim your <strong>Tenderstem broccoli</strong>, then add<strong> </strong>to the middle of the foil with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tbsp] </span><strong>cold water </strong>and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>butter</strong></p><p>Scrunch the edges of the foil to form a sealed parcel[s] and put the tray[s] in the oven for 10-12 min or until the Tenderstem broccoli is tender with a slight bite</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1-1670922326373-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1-1670922326373-x400.jpg",
