            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1-1670922326373-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide based pan (preferably non-stick) with a small drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> chopped bacon</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until golden and crisp</p><p>Once done, transfer the <strong>crispy</strong> <strong>bacon</strong> to kitchen paper and set aside, reserving the pan</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1670922340029-x200.jpg",
